205/* 積算値読出し(OV) */
206void command_OV (short com_mode){
207
208 unsigned long long value;
209 unsigned short value_high;
210 unsigned short value_low;
211 unsigned short err_st;
212 char add[20] = {0};
213
214 strcat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma);
215 err_st = MAIN[ch_no[com_mode] -1].com_err_status; //エラーステータス
216 if(err_st == 0) mes_err[ch_no[com_mode]] = 0;
217 if(err_total_status((short)err_st) != B_YES){ //積算監視エラー以外
218 if(err_zero_status((short)err_st) != B_YES //ゼロ点調整エラー以外で、
219 && MAIN[ch_no[com_mode] -1].led_err_status == 0){ //エラー発生していない場合
220 MAIN[ch_no[com_mode] -1].com_err_status = (short)0; //エラーステータスを読込んだらクリア
221 }
222 }else{ //積算監視エラーが発生
223 if(err_zero_status((short)err_st) != B_YES){ //ゼロ点調整エラー以外で、
224 MAIN[ch_no[com_mode] -1].com_err_status = (short)0; //エラーステータスを読込んだらクリア
225 MAIN[ch_no[com_mode] -1].led_err_status = (short)0;
226 }
227 }
228
229 add[0] = err_st / 10 + 0x30;
230 add[1] = err_st % 10 + 0x30;
231 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],add,sizeof(add)); //最後尾に読込値追加
232 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
233 value = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].addit_buff.DWORD / 10000; //積算値x10000000 → x1000
234 read_change(com_mode,value,3,2);
235
236}
237
238/* 積算値読出し・積算中常時更新(ov) */
239void command_ov (short com_mode){
240
241 unsigned long long value;
242 unsigned short value_high;
243 unsigned short value_low;
244 unsigned short err_st;
245 char add[20] = {0};
246
247 strcat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma);
248 err_st = MAIN[ch_no[com_mode] -1].com_err_status; //エラーステータス
249 if(err_st == 0) mes_err[ch_no[com_mode]] = 0;
250 if(err_total_status((short)err_st) != B_YES){ //積算監視エラー以外
251 if(err_zero_status((short)err_st) != B_YES //ゼロ点調整エラー以外で、
252 && MAIN[ch_no[com_mode] -1].led_err_status == 0){ //エラー発生していない場合
253 MAIN[ch_no[com_mode] -1].com_err_status = (short)0; //エラーステータスを読込んだらクリア
254 }
255 }else{ //積算監視エラーが発生
256 if(err_zero_status((short)err_st) != B_YES){ //ゼロ点調整エラー以外で、
257 MAIN[ch_no[com_mode] -1].com_err_status = (short)0; //エラーステータスを読込んだらクリア
258 MAIN[ch_no[com_mode] -1].led_err_status = (short)0;
259 }
260 }
261
262 add[0] = err_st / 10 + 0x30;
263 add[1] = err_st % 10 + 0x30;
264 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],add,sizeof(add)); //最後尾に読込値追加
265 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
266 value = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].addit_buff_ov.UINT64 / 10000; //積算値x10000000 → x1000
267 read_change(com_mode,value,3,2);
268
269}

271/* 瞬時流量1点読出し(OE) */
272void command_OE(short com_mode){
273
274 short m;
275 short l;
276 short ch_z;
277 short ch_number;
278 char ch[1] = {0};
279
280 unsigned short err_st;
281 short mes_err_cnt[7] = {0};
282 long flow;
283 unsigned long flow_z;
284 unsigned long flow_cal;
285 unsigned char flow_1;
286
287 flow_check[com_mode] = 1;
288 ch[0] = RX_buf[com_mode][7]; //CH数判定
289 ch_z = ch[0] - 0x30;
290 TX_buf[com_mode][8] = RX_buf[com_mode][6];
291 TX_buf[com_mode][9] = RX_buf[com_mode][7];
292
293 for (m = 0; m < ch_z; m++){
294 ch[0] = RX_buf[com_mode][9 + 2*m]; //CH番号判定
295 ch_number = ch[0] - 0x30;
296 TX_buf[com_mode][10 + 9*m] = RX_buf[com_mode][8 + 2*m];
297 TX_buf[com_mode][11 + 9*m] = RX_buf[com_mode][9 + 2*m];
298
299 err_st = MAIN[ch_number -1].com_err_status; //エラーステータス
300 if(err_st != 0){
301 mes_err_cnt[ch_no[com_mode]]++;
302 mes_err_cnt[ch_number]++;
303 }
304 if(err_total_status((short)err_st) != B_YES){ //積算監視エラー以外
305 if(err_zero_status((short)err_st) != B_YES //ゼロ点調整エラー以外で、
306 && MAIN[ch_number -1].led_err_status == 0){ //エラー発生していない場合
307 MAIN[ch_number -1].com_err_status = (short)0; //エラーステータスを読込んだらクリア
308 }
309 }else{ //積算監視エラーが発生
310 if(err_zero_status((short)err_st) != B_YES){ //ゼロ点調整エラー以外で、
311 MAIN[ch_number -1].com_err_status = (short)0; //エラーステータスを読込んだらクリア
312 MAIN[ch_number -1].led_err_status = (short)0;
313 }
314 }
315
316 TX_buf[com_mode][12 + 9*m] = err_st / 10 + 0x30;
317 TX_buf[com_mode][13 + 9*m] = err_st % 10 + 0x30;
318
319 flow = MES[ch_number -1].ml_min_now; //瞬時流量値
320
321 if (flow >= 0) { flow_1 = 0x20; flow_z = flow;}
322 else { flow_1 = 0xA0; flow_z = flow * (-1);}
323
324 flow_cal = flow_z / 0x01000000;
325 if (flow_cal == 0x40 || flow_cal == 0x0D) {flow_cal++; flow_1 += 8;}
326 TX_buf[com_mode][15 + 9*m] = flow_cal;
327
328 flow_cal = flow_z % 0x01000000;
329 flow_cal /= 0x00010000;
330 if (flow_cal == 0x40 || flow_cal == 0x0D) {flow_cal++; flow_1 += 4;}
331 TX_buf[com_mode][16 + 9*m] = flow_cal;
332
333 flow_cal = flow_z % 0x00010000;
334 flow_cal /= 0x00000100;
335 if (flow_cal == 0x40 || flow_cal == 0x0D) {flow_cal++; flow_1 += 2;}
336 TX_buf[com_mode][17 + 9*m] = flow_cal;
337
338 flow_cal = flow_z % 0x00000100;
339 if (flow_cal == 0x40 || flow_cal == 0x0D) {flow_cal++; flow_1 += 1;}
340 TX_buf[com_mode][18 + 9*m] = flow_cal;
341
342 TX_buf[com_mode][14 + 9*m] = flow_1;
343 }
344 for (m = 0; m < 7; m++){
345 if(mes_err_cnt[m] == 0) mes_err[m] = 0;
346 }
347 ch[0] = 0;
348
349}
350
351/* 瞬時流量10点読出し(OQ) */
352void command_OQ (short com_mode){
353
354 short m;
355 short l;
356 short ch_z;
357 short ch_number;
358 char ch[1] = {0};
359
360 unsigned short err_st;
361 short mes_err_cnt[7] = {0};
362 long flow;
363 unsigned long flow_z;
364 unsigned long flow_cal;
365 unsigned char flow_1;
366
367 flow_check[com_mode] = 2;
368 ch[0] = RX_buf[com_mode][7]; //CH数判定
369 ch_z = ch[0] - 0x30;
370 TX_buf[com_mode][8] = RX_buf[com_mode][6];
371 TX_buf[com_mode][9] = RX_buf[com_mode][7];
372
373 for (m = 0; m < ch_z; m++){
374 ch[0] = RX_buf[com_mode][9 + 2*m]; //CH番号判定
375 ch_number = ch[0] - 0x30;
376 TX_buf[com_mode][10 + 72*m] = RX_buf[com_mode][8 + 2*m];
377 TX_buf[com_mode][11 + 72*m] = RX_buf[com_mode][9 + 2*m];
378 for (l = 0; l < 10; l++){
379 err_st = 0;
380 if(l >= MES[ch_number -1].past_flow_cnt){ //10点データバッファに10点なし
381 err_st = ERR_10POINT;
382 }
383 //優先順位が10点データ無効より高いエラーがある場合
384 if((MAIN[ch_number -1].com_err_status != 0) &&
385 (err_inf[MAIN[ch_number -1].com_err_status].err_priority < err_inf[ERR_10POINT].err_priority)){
386 err_st = MAIN[ch_number -1].com_err_status; //エラーステータス
387 }
388 if(err_st != 0){
389 mes_err_cnt[ch_no[com_mode]]++;
390 mes_err_cnt[ch_number]++;
391 }
392 if(err_total_status((short)err_st) != B_YES){ //積算監視エラー以外
393 if(err_zero_status((short)err_st) != B_YES //ゼロ点調整エラー以外で、
394 && MAIN[ch_number -1].led_err_status == 0){ //エラー発生していない場合
395 MAIN[ch_number -1].com_err_status = (short)0; //エラーステータスを読込んだらクリア
396 }
397 }else{ //積算監視エラーが発生
398 if(err_zero_status((short)err_st) != B_YES){ //ゼロ点調整エラー以外で、
399 MAIN[ch_number -1].com_err_status = (short)0; //エラーステータスを読込んだらクリア
400 MAIN[ch_number -1].led_err_status = (short)0;
401 }
402 }
403
404 TX_buf[com_mode][12 + 72*m + 7*l] = err_st / 10 + 0x30;
405 TX_buf[com_mode][13 + 72*m + 7*l] = err_st % 10 + 0x30;
406
407 flow = MES[ch_number -1].past_flow[l];
408
409 if (flow >= 0) { flow_1 = 0x20; flow_z = flow;}
410 else { flow_1 = 0xA0; flow_z = flow * (-1);}
411
412 flow_cal = flow_z / 0x01000000;
413 if (flow_cal == 0x40 || flow_cal == 0x0D) {flow_cal++; flow_1 += 8;}
414 TX_buf[com_mode][15 + 72*m + 7*l] = flow_cal;
415
416 flow_cal = flow_z % 0x01000000;
417 flow_cal /= 0x00010000;
418 if (flow_cal == 0x40 || flow_cal == 0x0D) {flow_cal++; flow_1 += 4;}
419 TX_buf[com_mode][16 + 72*m + 7*l] = flow_cal;
420
421 flow_cal = flow_z % 0x00010000;
422 flow_cal /= 0x00000100;
423 if (flow_cal == 0x40 || flow_cal == 0x0D) {flow_cal++; flow_1 += 2;}
424 TX_buf[com_mode][17 + 72*m + 7*l] = flow_cal;
425
426 flow_cal = flow_z % 0x00000100;
427 if (flow_cal == 0x40 || flow_cal == 0x0D) {flow_cal++; flow_1 += 1;}
428 TX_buf[com_mode][18 + 72*m + 7*l] = flow_cal;
429
430 TX_buf[com_mode][14 + 72*m + 7*l] = flow_1;
431
432 }
433 if(MES[ch_number -1].past_flow_cnt < 10){ //10点データバッファに10点なし
434 MES[ch_number -1].err_status |= ERR_JUDGE_10POINT; //10点データ無効エラーセット
435 }
436 MES[ch_number -1].past_flow_cnt = 0; //10点データ保存カウンタクリア
437 }
438 for (m = 0; m < 7; m++){
439 if(mes_err_cnt[m] == 0) mes_err[m] = 0;
440 }
441 ch[0] = 0;
442}
443
444/* 瞬時流量10点読出し・ローカットオフ(oq) */
445void command_oq (short com_mode){
446
447 short m;
448 short l;
449 short ch_z;
450 short ch_number;
451 char ch[1] = {0};
452
453 unsigned short err_st;
454 short mes_err_cnt[7] = {0};
455 long flow;
456 unsigned long flow_z;
457 unsigned long flow_cal;
458 unsigned char flow_1;
459
460 flow_check[com_mode] = 2;
461 ch[0] = RX_buf[com_mode][7]; //CH数判定
462 ch_z = ch[0] - 0x30;
463 TX_buf[com_mode][8] = RX_buf[com_mode][6];
464 TX_buf[com_mode][9] = RX_buf[com_mode][7];
465
466 for (m = 0; m < ch_z; m++){
467 ch[0] = RX_buf[com_mode][9 + 2*m]; //CH番号判定
468 ch_number = ch[0] - 0x30;
469 TX_buf[com_mode][10 + 72*m] = RX_buf[com_mode][8 + 2*m];
470 TX_buf[com_mode][11 + 72*m] = RX_buf[com_mode][9 + 2*m];
471 for (l = 0; l < 10; l++){
472 err_st = 0;
473 if(l >= MES[ch_number -1].past_flow_cnt){ //10点データバッファに10点なし
474 err_st = ERR_10POINT;
475 }
476 //優先順位が10点データ無効より高いエラーがある場合
477 if((MAIN[ch_number -1].com_err_status != 0) &&
478 (err_inf[MAIN[ch_number -1].com_err_status].err_priority < err_inf[ERR_10POINT].err_priority)){
479 err_st = MAIN[ch_number -1].com_err_status; //エラーステータス
480 }
481 if(err_st != 0){
482 mes_err_cnt[ch_no[com_mode]]++;
483 mes_err_cnt[ch_number]++;
484 }
485 if(err_total_status((short)err_st) != B_YES){ //積算監視エラー以外
486 if(err_zero_status((short)err_st) != B_YES //ゼロ点調整エラー以外で、
487 && MAIN[ch_number -1].led_err_status == 0){ //エラー発生していない場合
488 MAIN[ch_number -1].com_err_status = (short)0; //エラーステータスを読込んだらクリア
489 }
490 }else{ //積算監視エラーが発生
491 if(err_zero_status((short)err_st) != B_YES){ //ゼロ点調整エラー以外で、
492 MAIN[ch_number -1].com_err_status = (short)0; //エラーステータスを読込んだらクリア
493 MAIN[ch_number -1].led_err_status = (short)0;
494 }
495 }
496 TX_buf[com_mode][12 + 72*m + 7*l] = err_st / 10 + 0x30;
497 TX_buf[com_mode][13 + 72*m + 7*l] = err_st % 10 + 0x30;
498
499 flow = MES[ch_number -1].past_flow_oq[l];
500
501 if (flow >= 0) { flow_1 = 0x20; flow_z = flow;}
502 else { flow_1 = 0xA0; flow_z = flow * (-1);}
503
504 flow_cal = flow_z / 0x01000000;
505 if (flow_cal == 0x40 || flow_cal == 0x0D) {flow_cal++; flow_1 += 8;}
506 TX_buf[com_mode][15 + 72*m + 7*l] = flow_cal;
507
508 flow_cal = flow_z % 0x01000000;
509 flow_cal /= 0x00010000;
510 if (flow_cal == 0x40 || flow_cal == 0x0D) {flow_cal++; flow_1 += 4;}
511 TX_buf[com_mode][16 + 72*m + 7*l] = flow_cal;
512
513 flow_cal = flow_z % 0x00010000;
514 flow_cal /= 0x00000100;
515 if (flow_cal == 0x40 || flow_cal == 0x0D) {flow_cal++; flow_1 += 2;}
516 TX_buf[com_mode][17 + 72*m + 7*l] = flow_cal;
517
518 flow_cal = flow_z % 0x00000100;
519 if (flow_cal == 0x40 || flow_cal == 0x0D) {flow_cal++; flow_1 += 1;}
520 TX_buf[com_mode][18 + 72*m + 7*l] = flow_cal;
521
522 TX_buf[com_mode][14 + 72*m + 7*l] = flow_1;
523 }
524 if(MES[ch_number -1].past_flow_cnt < 10){ //10点データバッファに10点なし
525 MES[ch_number -1].err_status |= ERR_JUDGE_10POINT; //10点データ無効エラーセット
526 }
527 MES[ch_number -1].past_flow_cnt = 0; //10点データ保存カウンタクリア
528 }
529 for (m = 0; m < 7; m++){
530 if(mes_err_cnt[m] == 0) mes_err[m] = 0;
531 }
532 ch[0] = 0;
533}
534
535/* ステータス読出し(SFC9000対応)(RS) */
536void command_RS (short com_mode){
537
538 short m;
539 short ch_z;
540 short ch_number;
541 unsigned short err_st;
542 short mes_err_cnt[7] = {0};
543 char ch[1] = {0};
544 char add[20] = {0};
545
546/* シングルコマンド */
547 if (ch_no[com_mode] >=1 && ch_no[com_mode] <=6){
548 /* 動作ステータス */
549 add[0] = MAIN[ch_no[com_mode] -1].com_act_status / 10 + 0x30;
550 add[1] = MAIN[ch_no[com_mode] -1].com_act_status % 10 + 0x30;
551 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],add,sizeof(add));
552 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
553 /* エラーステータス */
554 add[0] = MAIN[ch_no[com_mode] -1].com_err_status / 10 + 0x30;
555 add[1] = MAIN[ch_no[com_mode] -1].com_err_status % 10 + 0x30;
556 err_st = MAIN[ch_no[com_mode] -1].com_err_status;
557 if(err_st == 0) mes_err[ch_no[com_mode]] = 0;
558 if(err_total_status((short)err_st) != B_YES){ //積算監視エラー以外
559 if(err_zero_status((short)err_st) != B_YES //ゼロ点調整エラー以外で、
560 && MAIN[ch_no[com_mode] -1].led_err_status == 0){ //エラー発生していない場合
561 MAIN[ch_no[com_mode] -1].com_err_status = (short)0; //エラーステータスを読込んだらクリア
562 }
563 }else{ //積算監視エラーが発生
564 if(err_zero_status((short)err_st) != B_YES){ //ゼロ点調整エラー以外で、
565 MAIN[ch_no[com_mode] -1].com_err_status = (short)0; //エラーステータスを読込んだらクリア
566 MAIN[ch_no[com_mode] -1].led_err_status = (short)0;
567 }
568 }
569 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],add,sizeof(add));
570 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
571 /* 再起動ステータス */
572 err_st = reset_factor;
573 read_change0X_2digit_status(com_mode,err_st);
574 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
575 /* CUnetエラーステータス */
576 err_st = send_err_status;
577 read_change0X_2digit_status(com_mode,err_st);
578 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
579 /* CUnet MCARE/LCARE情報 */
580 err_st = cunet_mcare;
581 read_change0X_status(com_mode,err_st);
582 }
583/* マルチコマンド */
584 else if (ch_no[com_mode] == 0){
585 ch[0] = RX_buf[com_mode][7]; //CH数判定
586 ch_z = ch[0] - 0x30;
587 ch[0] = 0;
588 for (m = 0; m <= ch_z; m++){
589 TX_buf[com_mode][8 + 2*m] = RX_buf[com_mode][6 + 2*m];
590 TX_buf[com_mode][9 + 2*m] = RX_buf[com_mode][7 + 2*m];
591 }
592 for (m = 0; m < ch_z; m++){
593 ch[0] = RX_buf[com_mode][9 + 2*m]; //CH番号判定
594 ch_number = ch[0] - 0x30;
595 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
596 /* 動作ステータス */
597 add[0] = MAIN[ch_number -1].com_act_status / 10 + 0x30;
598 add[1] = MAIN[ch_number -1].com_act_status % 10 + 0x30;
599 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],add,sizeof(add));
600 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
601 /* エラーステータス */
602 add[0] = MAIN[ch_number -1].com_err_status / 10 + 0x30;
603 add[1] = MAIN[ch_number -1].com_err_status % 10 + 0x30;
604 err_st = MAIN[ch_number -1].com_err_status;
605 if(err_st != 0){
606 mes_err_cnt[ch_no[com_mode]]++;
607 mes_err_cnt[ch_number]++;
608 }
609 if(err_total_status((short)err_st) != B_YES){ //積算監視エラー以外
610 if(err_zero_status((short)err_st) != B_YES //ゼロ点調整エラー以外で、
611 && MAIN[ch_number -1].led_err_status == 0){ //エラー発生していない場合
612 MAIN[ch_number -1].com_err_status = (short)0; //エラーステータスを読込んだらクリア
613 }
614 }else{ //積算監視エラーが発生
615 if(err_zero_status((short)err_st) != B_YES){ //ゼロ点調整エラー以外で、
616 MAIN[ch_number -1].com_err_status = (short)0; //エラーステータスを読込んだらクリア
617 MAIN[ch_number -1].led_err_status = (short)0;
618 }
619 }
620 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],add,sizeof(add));
621 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
622 /* 再起動ステータス */
623 err_st = reset_factor;
624 read_change0X_2digit_status(com_mode,err_st);
625 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
626 /* CUnetエラーステータス */
627 err_st = send_err_status;
628 read_change0X_2digit_status(com_mode,err_st);
629 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
630 /* CUnet MCARE/LCARE情報 */
631 err_st = cunet_mcare;
632 read_change0X_status(com_mode,err_st);
633 }
634 for (m = 0; m < 7; m++){
635 if(mes_err_cnt[m] == 0) mes_err[m] = 0;
636 }
637 }
638
639}
640

694 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
695 /* エラーステータス */
696 add[0] = MAIN[ch_number -1].com_err_status / 10 + 0x30;

698 err_st = MAIN[ch_number -1].com_err_status;
699 if(err_st != 0){
700 mes_err_cnt[ch_no[com_mode]]++;
701 mes_err_cnt[ch_number]++;
702 }
703 if(err_total_status((short)err_st) != B_YES){ //積算監視エラー以外
704 if(err_zero_status((short)err_st) != B_YES //ゼロ点調整エラー以外で、
705 && MAIN[ch_number -1].led_err_status == 0){ //エラー発生していない場合
706 MAIN[ch_number -1].com_err_status = (short)0; //エラーステータスを読込んだらクリア
707 }
708 }else{ //積算監視エラーが発生
709 if(err_zero_status((short)err_st) != B_YES){ //ゼロ点調整エラー以外で、
710 MAIN[ch_number -1].com_err_status = (short)0; //エラーステータスを読込んだらクリア
711 MAIN[ch_number -1].led_err_status = (short)0;
712 }
713 }
714 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],add,sizeof(add));
715 }
716 for (m = 0; m < 7; m++){
717 if(mes_err_cnt[m] == 0) mes_err[m] = 0;
718 }
719 }
720
721 }

829/* ユーザーリニアライズ読出し(Ru) */
830void command_Ru (short com_mode){
831
832 short l;
833 unsigned short *pt;
834 long value;
835 unsigned short value_high;
836 unsigned short value_low;
837
838 short point;
839
840 point = (short)(SVD[ch_no[com_mode]-1].uslnr_num >> 8) & 0x00FF; /*設定点数取得*/
841 read_change(com_mode,point,0,0);
842 pt = &SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].uslnr_out1.WORD.low;
843 for (l = 0; l < 15; l++){
844 value_low = *pt;
845 pt++;
846 value_high = *pt;
847 value = value_low + value_high * 0x10000;
848 read_change(com_mode,value,1,1);
849 pt++;
850 }
851 pt = &SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].uslnr_in1.WORD.low;
852 for (l = 0; l < 15; l++){
853 value_low = *pt;
854 pt++;
855 value_high = *pt;
856 value = value_low + value_high * 0x10000;
857 read_change(com_mode,value,1,1);
858 pt++;
859 }
860
861}

879 pt++;

882 read_change(com_mode,value,3,1);
883 pt++;
884 }
885 pt = &SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].mklnr_in1.WORD.low;

925 }

928 ch[0] = RX_buf[com_mode][7]; //CH数判定

933 TX_buf[com_mode][9 + 2*m] = RX_buf[com_mode][7 + 2*m];
934 }
935 for (m = 0; m < ch_z; m++){

937 ch_number = ch[0] - 0x30;

948/* バージョン値読出し(SFC9000対応)(RF) */
949void command_RF (short com_mode){
950
951 short l;
952 unsigned long value;
953 unsigned short *pt;
954 short sn_version;
955 short sn_ver_cal;
956 char add[20] = {0};
957
958 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].soft_ver; //software version
959 read_change0X_version(com_mode,value);
960 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
961
962 if(com_type == COM_RS485){
963 value = 0;
964 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
965 }
966 else{
967 value = 1;
968 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
969 }
970
971 pt = &SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].c_serial[0]; //シリアルナンバー
972 for (l = 0; l < 8; l++){
973 sn_version = *pt;
974 sn_ver_cal = sn_version / 0x0100;
975 if ( (sn_ver_cal >= 0x30 && sn_ver_cal <= 0x39) || (sn_ver_cal >= 0x41 && sn_ver_cal <= 0x5A) ){ //0-9orA-Z
976 add[2*l] = sn_ver_cal;
977 }
978 sn_ver_cal = sn_version % 0x0100;
979 if ( (sn_ver_cal >= 0x30 && sn_ver_cal <= 0x39) || (sn_ver_cal >= 0x41 && sn_ver_cal <= 0x5A) ){ //0-9orA-Z
980 add[2*l + 1] = sn_ver_cal;
981 }
982 pt++;
983 }
984 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],add,sizeof(add));
985
986 if(com_type == COM_RS485){
987 value = 0;
988 read_change(com_mode,value,0,1);
989 }
990 else{
991 value = disp_cunet_read();
992 read_change(com_mode,value,0,1);
993 }
994
995}

997/* バージョン値読出し(RV) */
998 void command_RV (short com_mode){
999
1000 unsigned long value;
1001
1002 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].soft_ver; //software version
1003 read_change0X_versionRV(com_mode,value);
1004 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
1005
1006 // value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].hard_ver; //hardware version
1007 value = FPGA_VERSION; //FPGA version
1008 read_change0X_versionRV(com_mode,value);
1009
1010 }
1011
1012/* ログデータ読出し(RG)(SFC9000対応) */
1013void command_RG (short com_mode){
1014
1015 short l;
1016 short ch_z;
1017 unsigned short *pt;
1018 char ch[1] = {0};
1019 char add[20] = {0};
1020 long value;
1021 long long diff;
1022 unsigned short err_st;
1023 unsigned long long addit;
1024
1025 TX_buf[com_mode][9] = RX_buf[com_mode][6];
1026 TX_buf[com_mode][10] = RX_buf[com_mode][7];
1027 ch[0] = RX_buf[com_mode][7]; //ログ履歴番号判定
1028 ch_z = ch[0] - 0x30;
1029 if(ch_z == 0){ch_z = 10;}
1030 ch[0] = 0;
1031
1032 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
1033
1034 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].pwon_count; //現在電源ON回数
1035 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1036
1037 value = cmi_count; //現在エラータイマー
1038 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1039
1040 value = LOG_DETAIL[ch_no[com_mode] -1][ch_z -1].err_pwon_count; //発生時電源ON回数
1041 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1042
1043 value = LOG_DETAIL[ch_no[com_mode] -1][ch_z -1].err_time; //発生時エラータイマー
1044 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1045
1046 add[0] = LOG_DETAIL[ch_no[com_mode] -1][ch_z -1].err_code / 10 + 0x30; //ErrorLogCode
1047 add[1] = LOG_DETAIL[ch_no[com_mode] -1][ch_z -1].err_code % 10 + 0x30;
1048 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],add,sizeof(add)); //最後尾に読込値追加
1049 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
1050
1051 value = LOG_DETAIL[ch_no[com_mode] -1][ch_z -1].flow_quantity; //流量
1052 read_change(com_mode,value,2,2);
1053
1054 value = LOG_DETAIL[ch_no[com_mode] -1][ch_z -1].flow_velocity; //流速
1055 read_change(com_mode,value,3,2);
1056
1057 value = LOG_DETAIL[ch_no[com_mode] -1][ch_z -1].sound_speed; //音速
1058 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1059
1060 addit = LOG_DETAIL[ch_no[com_mode] -1][ch_z -1].total_count.DWORD / 10000; //積算値
1061 read_change(com_mode,addit,3,2);
1062
1063 value = LOG_DETAIL[ch_no[com_mode] -1][ch_z -1].wave_max; //受波波形最大値
1064 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1065
1066 value = LOG_DETAIL[ch_no[com_mode] -1][ch_z -1].wave_min; //受波波形最小値
1067 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1068
1069 diff = LOG_DETAIL[ch_no[com_mode] -1][ch_z -1].dt * 32; //伝搬時間差
1070 if (diff > 99999999) {diff = 99999999;}
1071 else if (diff < -99999999) {diff = -99999999;}
1072 read_change(com_mode,diff,0,2);
1073
1074 value = LOG_DETAIL[ch_no[com_mode] -1][ch_z -1].correlate; //相関値幅
1075 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1076
1077 value = LOG_DETAIL[ch_no[com_mode] -1][ch_z -1].zero_offset; //ゼロ点オフセット
1078 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1079
1080 err_st = LOG_DETAIL[ch_no[com_mode] -1][ch_z -1].status; //status
1081 read_change0X_status(com_mode,err_st);
1082 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
1083
1084 value = LOG_DETAIL[ch_no[com_mode] -1][ch_z -1].fifo_position; //FIFO受波波形検出位置
1085 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1086
1087 value = LOG_DETAIL[ch_no[com_mode] -1][ch_z -1].gain_up; //Gain 1st stage
1088 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1089
1090 value = LOG_DETAIL[ch_no[com_mode] -1][ch_z -1].gain_down; //Gain 2nd stage
1091 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1092
1093 value = LOG_DETAIL[ch_no[com_mode] -1][ch_z -1].fifo_ch; //FIFO CH
1094 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1095
1096 value = LOG_DETAIL[ch_no[com_mode] -1][ch_z -1].p1_p2; //受波の差(P1-P2)
1097 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1098
1099 err_st = reset_factor; //再起動ステータス
1100 read_change0X_2digit_status(com_mode,err_st);
1101 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
1102
1103 err_st = LOG_DETAIL[ch_no[com_mode] -1][ch_z -1].mail_err_status; //CUnetエラーステータス
1104 read_change0X_2digit_status(com_mode,err_st);
1105 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
1106
1107 err_st = cunet_mcare; //CUnet MCARE/LCARE情報
1108 read_change0X_status(com_mode,err_st);
1109 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
1110
1111 err_st = cunet_mfr1; //CUnet MFR情報
1112 read_change0X_status(com_mode,err_st);
1113 err_st = cunet_mfr2;
1114 read_change0X_status(com_mode,err_st);
1115 err_st = cunet_mfr3;
1116 read_change0X_status(com_mode,err_st);
1117 err_st = cunet_mfr4;
1118 read_change0X_status(com_mode,err_st);
1119
1120 pt = &LOG_DETAIL[ch_no[com_mode] -1][ch_z -1].sum_abs_log[0];
1121 for (l = 0; l < 40; l++){
1122 value = *pt;
1123 read_change(com_mode,value,0,1);
1124 pt++;
1125 }
1126
1127}

1188 else if (diff < -99999999) {diff = -99999999;}

1214 read_change(com_mode,value,0,0);

1222/* ゼロ調整データ読出し(SFC9000対応)(RD) */
1223void command_RD (short com_mode){
1224
1225 short m;
1226 short l;
1227 short ch_z;
1228 short ch_number;
1229 char ch[1] = {0};
1230 long value;
1231 long long diff;
1232
1233 ch[0] = RX_buf[com_mode][7]; //CH数判定
1234 ch_z = ch[0] - 0x30;
1235 ch[0] = 0;
1236 for (m = 0; m <= ch_z; m++){
1237 TX_buf[com_mode][8 + 2*m] = RX_buf[com_mode][6 + 2*m];
1238 TX_buf[com_mode][9 + 2*m] = RX_buf[com_mode][7 + 2*m];
1239 }
1240 for (m = 0; m < ch_z; m++){
1241 ch[0] = RX_buf[com_mode][9 + 2*m]; //CH番号判定
1242 ch_number = ch[0] - 0x30;
1243
1244 value = SVD[ch_number -1].viscos; //動粘度
1245 read_change(com_mode,value,2,1);
1246
1247 value = SVD[ch_number -1].zero_wave_max; //受波波形最大値
1248 read_change(com_mode,value,0,1);
1249
1250 value = SVD[ch_number -1].zero_wave_min; //受波波形最小値
1251 read_change(com_mode,value,0,1);
1252
1253 diff = SVD[ch_number -1].zero_delta_ts.DWORD * 32; //伝搬時間差
1254 if (diff > 99999999) {diff = 99999999;}
1255 else if (diff < -99999999) {diff = -99999999;}
1256 read_change(com_mode,diff,0,1);
1257
1258 value = SVD[ch_number -1].zero_fifo_pos; //FIFO受波波形検出位置
1259 read_change(com_mode,value,0,1);
1260
1261 value = SVD[ch_number -1].zero_gain_1st; //Gain1
1262 read_change(com_mode,value,0,1);
1263
1264 value = SVD[ch_number -1].zero_gain_2nd; //Gain2
1265 read_change(com_mode,value,0,1);
1266
1267 value = SVD[ch_number -1].zero_p1p2; //受波の差(P1-P2)
1268 read_change(com_mode,value,0,1);
1269 }
1270
1271}

1424/* メーカー設定読出し(R1) */
1425 void command_R1 (short com_mode){
1426
1427 short l;
1428 short value;
1429 unsigned short *pt;
1430 short sn_version;
1431 short sn_ver_cal;
1432 char add[20] = {0};
1433
1434 value = 0; //補正10%（該当データなし）
1435 read_change(com_mode,value,2,2);
1436
1437 value = 0; //補正25%（該当データなし）
1438 read_change(com_mode,value,2,2);
1439
1440 value = 0; //補正50%（該当データなし）
1441 read_change(com_mode,value,2,2);
1442
1443 value = 0; //補正75%（該当データなし）
1444 read_change(com_mode,value,2,2);
1445
1446 value = 0; //補正100%（該当データなし）
1447 read_change(com_mode,value,2,2);
1448
1449 pt = &SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].c_serial[0]; //シリアルナンバー
1450 for (l = 0; l < 8; l++){
1451 sn_version = *pt;
1452 sn_ver_cal = sn_version / 0x0100;
1453 if ( (sn_ver_cal >= 0x30 && sn_ver_cal <= 0x39) || (sn_ver_cal >= 0x41 && sn_ver_cal <= 0x5A) ){ //0-9orA-Z
1454 add[2*l] = sn_ver_cal;
1455 }
1456 sn_ver_cal = sn_version % 0x0100;
1457 if ( (sn_ver_cal >= 0x30 && sn_ver_cal <= 0x39) || (sn_ver_cal >= 0x41 && sn_ver_cal <= 0x5A) ){ //0-9orA-Z
1458 add[2*l + 1] = sn_ver_cal;
1459 }
1460 pt++;
1461 }
1462 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],add,sizeof(add));
1463
1464 }
1465

1476

1478 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1479

1483 }
1484
1485/*******************************************
1486 * Function : command_R3
1487 * Summary : ゼロクロス測定データ読み出し
1488 * Argument :
1489 * Return :
1490 * Caution : None
1491 * Note : 差分相関測定データ読み出しはR7
1492 * *****************************************/
1493 void command_R3 (short com_mode){
1494
1495 short l;
1496 long value;
1497 long long diff;
1498 unsigned long long addit;
1499 short pch = ch_no[com_mode] - 1;
1500 float TimDif;
1501
1502 if(RX_buf[com_mode][7] != '0'){ //測定時データ
1503 TX_buf[com_mode][9] = RX_buf[com_mode][7];
1504 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
1505
1506 //1. 流量[mL/min]
1507 value = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].ml_min_now;
1508 read_change(com_mode,value,2,2);
1509
1510 //2. 流速[m/s]
1511 value = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].flow_vel_c / 100;
1512 read_change(com_mode,value,3,2);
1513
1514 //3. 音速[m/s]
1515 value = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].sound_vel_f * 100;
1516 read_change(com_mode,value,2,2);
1517
1518 //4. 積算値[mL/min]
1519 addit = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].addit_buff.DWORD / 10000;
1520 read_change(com_mode,addit,3,2);
1521
1522 //5. UP伝搬時間[us]
1523 TimDif = GetTimDif(pch, 0);
1524 read_change(com_mode, TimDif * 1000.0, 3, ADD_CMM_AFR_VAL);
1525
1526 //6. DN伝搬時間[us]
1527 TimDif = GetTimDif(pch, 1);
1528 read_change(com_mode, TimDif * 1000.0, 3, ADD_CMM_AFR_VAL);
1529
1530 //7. 伝搬時間差[ps]
1531 diff = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].delta_ts_zero * 32;
1532 if (diff > 99999999) {diff = 99999999;}
1533 else if (diff < -99999999) {diff = -99999999;}
1534 read_change(com_mode,diff,0,2);
1535
1536 //8. UP無駄時間[ps]
1537 value = MES[pch].FwdSurplsTim;
1538 read_change(com_mode,value, 0, ADD_CMM_AFR_VAL);
1539
1540 //9. DN無駄時間[ps]
1541 value = MES[pch].RevSurplsTim;
1542 read_change(com_mode,value, 0, ADD_CMM_AFR_VAL);
1543
1544 //10. status
1545 value = MAIN[ch_no[com_mode] -1].err_condition;
1546 read_change0X_status(com_mode,value);
1547 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
1548
1549 //11. Window Position[us]
1550 value = ((MES[pch].fifo_ch_read & 0xFF) << 8);
1551 value += (MES[pch].fifo_no_read & 0xFF);
1552 read_change(com_mode,value, 0, ADD_CMM_AFR_VAL);
1553
1554 //12. Gain 1st stage(未使用)
1555 value = get_attenuator_gain(ch_no[com_mode]-1);
1556 read_change(com_mode,value, 0, ADD_CMM_AFR_VAL);
1557
1558 //13. Gain 2nd stage
1559 value = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].amp_gain_for;
1560 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1561
1562 //14. Peak[mV] (おそらくアンプ増幅後は512mVが最大)
1563 // value = 512 * (MES[pch].rev_max_data - AD_BASE_UNIT) / 4095;
1564 value = 512 * (MES[pch].rev_max_data - AD_BASE_UNIT) / AD_MAX_UNIT;
1565 read_change(com_mode,value, 0, ADD_CMM_AFR_VAL);
1566
1567 //15. 打ち込み周波数(014Eでは打ち込み周波数を表示)
1568 value = SVD[pch].drive_freq;
1569 read_change(com_mode,value, 0, ADD_NO_CMM);
1570
1571 //16-25. 上流波形ピーク位置
1572 for (l = 0; l < WAV_PEK_NUM / 2; l++){
1573 value = MES[pch].FwdWavMaxPekPosLst[l];
1574 read_change(com_mode, value, 0, ADD_CMM_BFR_VAL);
1575 value = MES[pch].FwdWavMinPekPosLst[l];
1576 read_change(com_mode, value, 0, ADD_CMM_BFR_VAL);
1577 }
1578
1579 //26-35. 上流波形ピーク値
1580 for (l = 0; l < WAV_PEK_NUM / 2; l++){
1581 value = MES[pch].FwdWavMaxPekValLst[l];
1582 read_change(com_mode,value, 0, ADD_CMM_BFR_VAL);
1583 value = MES[pch].FwdWavMinPekValLst[l];
1584 read_change(com_mode,value, 0, ADD_CMM_BFR_VAL);
1585 }
1586
1587 //36-45. 下流波形ピーク位置
1588 for (l = 0; l < WAV_PEK_NUM / 2; l++){
1589 value = MES[pch].RevWavMaxPekPosLst[l];
1590 read_change(com_mode, value, 0, ADD_CMM_BFR_VAL);
1591 value = MES[pch].RevWavMinPekPosLst[l];
1592 read_change(com_mode, value, 0, ADD_CMM_BFR_VAL);
1593 }
1594
1595 //46-55. 上流波形ピーク位置
1596 for (l = 0; l < WAV_PEK_NUM / 2; l++){
1597 value = MES[pch].RevWavMaxPekValLst[l];
1598 read_change(com_mode,value, 0, ADD_CMM_BFR_VAL);
1599 value = MES[pch].RevWavMinPekValLst[l];
1600 read_change(com_mode,value, 0, ADD_CMM_BFR_VAL);
1601 }
1602 }else{ //ゼロ調整時データ
1603 TX_buf[com_mode][9] = RX_buf[com_mode][7];
1604 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
1605
1606 //1. 流量[mL/min]
1607 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_flow_qat.DWORD;
1608 read_change(com_mode,value,2,2);
1609
1610 //2. 流速[m/s]
1611 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_flow_vel.DWORD / 100;
1612 read_change(com_mode,value,3,2);
1613
1614 //3. 音速[m/s]
1615 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_sound_spd * 100;
1616 read_change(com_mode,value,2,2);
1617
1618 //4. 積算値[mL/min]
1619 addit = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_addit.DWORD / 10000;
1620 read_change(com_mode,addit,3,2);
1621
1622 //5. UP伝搬時間[ps]
1623 value = SVD[pch].zero_FwdTimDif.DWORD;
1624 read_change(com_mode,value, 3, ADD_CMM_AFR_VAL);
1625
1626 //6. DN伝搬時間[ps]
1627 value = SVD[pch].zero_RevTimDif.DWORD;
1628 read_change(com_mode,value, 3, ADD_CMM_AFR_VAL);
1629
1630 //7. 伝搬時間差[ps]
1631 diff = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_delta_ts.DWORD * 32;
1632 if (diff > 99999999) {diff = 99999999;}
1633 else if (diff < -99999999) {diff = -99999999;}
1634 read_change(com_mode,diff,0,2);
1635
1636 //8. UP無駄時間[ps]
1637 value = SVD[pch].zero_FwdSurplsTim;
1638 read_change(com_mode,value, 0, ADD_CMM_AFR_VAL);
1639
1640 //9. DN無駄時間[ps]
1641 value = SVD[pch].zero_RevSurplsTim;
1642 read_change(com_mode,value, 0, ADD_CMM_AFR_VAL);
1643
1644 //10. status
1645 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_condition;
1646 read_change0X_status(com_mode,value);
1647 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
1648
1649 //11. Window Position[us]
1650 value = ((SVD[pch].zero_fifo_ch & 0xFF) << 8);
1651 value += (SVD[pch].zero_fifo_pos & 0xFF);
1652 read_change(com_mode,value, 0, ADD_CMM_AFR_VAL);
1653
1654 //12. Gain 1st stage(未使用)
1655 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_gain_1st;
1656 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1657
1658 //13. Gain 2nd stage
1659 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_gain_2nd;
1660 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1661
1662 //14. Peak[mV]
1663 // value = 512 * (SVD[pch].zero_wave_max - AD_BASE_UNIT) / 4095;
1664 value = 512 * (SVD[pch].zero_wave_max - AD_BASE_UNIT) / AD_MAX_UNIT;
1665 read_change(com_mode,value, 0, ADD_CMM_AFR_VAL);
1666
1667 //15. 打ち込み周波数(014Eでは打ち込み周波数を表示)
1668 value = SVD[pch].zero_drive_freq;
1669 read_change(com_mode,value, 0, ADD_NO_CMM);
1670
1671 //16-25. 上流波形ピーク位置
1672 for (l = 0; l < WAV_PEK_NUM; l++){
1673 value = SVD[pch].zero_FwdWavPekPosLst[l];
1674 read_change(com_mode,value, 0, ADD_CMM_BFR_VAL);
1675 }
1676
1677 //26-35. 上流波形ピーク値
1678 for (l = 0; l < WAV_PEK_NUM; l++){
1679 value = SVD[pch].zero_FwdWavPekValLst[l];
1680 read_change(com_mode,value, 0, ADD_CMM_BFR_VAL);
1681 }
1682
1683 //36-45. 下流波形ピーク位置
1684 for (l = 0; l < WAV_PEK_NUM; l++){
1685 value = SVD[pch].zero_RevWavPekPosLst[l];
1686 read_change(com_mode,value, 0, ADD_CMM_BFR_VAL);
1687 }
1688
1689 //46-55. 上流波形ピーク位置
1690 for (l = 0; l < WAV_PEK_NUM; l++){
1691 value = SVD[pch].zero_RevWavPekValLst[l];
1692 read_change(com_mode,value, 0, ADD_CMM_BFR_VAL);
1693 }
1694 }
1695 }
1696#if defined(MESWAVEXP)
1697
1698/************************************************************
1699 * Fucntion : WavInBuff
1700 * Summary : 波形データを送信バッファに入れる
1701 * Argument : com_mode -> 通信モード
1702 * Return : void
1703 * Caution : なし
1704 * Note : command_R4, command_R8のコードを移植
1705 * ただし下記分岐は削除
1706 * if((MES[ch_no[com_mode]-1].err_status & ERR_JUDGE_EMPTY) != 0){ //Empty Sensor時 波形データ0
1707 * ofs = 3;
1708 * }
1709 * 理由 : ERR_FLOW_COUNT に ERR_JUDGE_EMPTY が含まれる
1710************************************************************/
1711void WavInBuff(short com_mode){
1712 short ofs;
1713 short l;
1714 short value;
1715
1716 if(MES[ch_no[com_mode]-1].wave_monitor_mode == 0 || //常に更新設定
1717 (MES[ch_no[com_mode]-1].err_status & ERR_FLOW_CONT) == 0){ //流量エラー無し
1718
1719 if(RX_buf[com_mode][8] == 0x2c){ // 0〜2はFWDのデータ
1720 ofs = RX_buf[com_mode][7] - '0';
1721 if(ofs == 0) {
1722 for(l = 0; l < MESWAVSIZ + 100; l++){
1723 fow_wave_data[l] = MES[ch_no[com_mode]-1].fow_data[l];
1724 }
1725 }
1726 }else{ // 10〜12はREVのデータ
1727 ofs = RX_buf[com_mode][8] - '0';
1728 if(ofs == 0) {
1729 for(l = 0; l < MESWAVSIZ + 100; l++){
1730 rev_wave_data[l] = MES[ch_no[com_mode]-1].rev_data[l];
1731 }
1732 }
1733 }
1734
1735 }
1736
1737 if(ofs <= (MESWAVSIZ / 100)) {
1738 for (l = 0; l < 100; l++){
1739 if(RX_buf[com_mode][8] == 0x2c){ //FWDデータ
1740// value = (fow_wave_data[(ofs*100)+l] - AD_BASE)/4; //受波波形データ
1741 value = (fow_wave_data[(ofs*100)+l] - AD_BASE)>>4; //受波波形データ(4回分加算してあるので更に4で割って1/16とする)
1742 }else{ //REVデータ
1743// value = (rev_wave_data[(ofs*100)+l] - AD_BASE)/4; //受波波形データ
1744 value = (rev_wave_data[(ofs*100)+l] - AD_BASE)>>4; //受波波形データ(4回分加算してあるので更に4で割って1/16とする)
1745 }
1746 read_change(com_mode,value,0,1);
1747 }
1748 }else{
1749 for (l = 0; l < 100; l++){
1750 value = 0; //波形データ0：無効Block(3〜9 or 13〜19)時 or Empty Sensor時処理
1751 read_change(com_mode,value,0,1);
1752 }
1753 }
1754}
1755#endif
1756
1757/* 測定波形読出し(R4) */
1758void command_R4 (short com_mode){
1759
1760 short l;
1761 short value;
1762 short *data;
1763 short ofs;
1764
1765 TX_buf[com_mode][9] = RX_buf[com_mode][7];
1766 if(RX_buf[com_mode][8] == 0x2c){ //Data block部が1文字の場合
1767 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma)); //最後尾に','追加
1768 TX_buf[com_mode][11] = '0';
1769 }else{ //Data block部が2文字の場合
1770 TX_buf[com_mode][10] = RX_buf[com_mode][8];
1771 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma)); //最後尾に','追加
1772 TX_buf[com_mode][12] = '0';
1773 }
1774#if 0
1775 for (l = 0; l < 100; l++){
1776 value = (MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].fow_data[l]-AD_BASE)/4; //受波波形データ
1777 read_change(com_mode,value,0,1);
1778 }
1779#else
1780
1781#if defined(MESWAVEXP)
1782 WavInBuff(com_mode);
1783#else
1784 if(MES[ch_no[com_mode]-1].wave_monitor_mode == 0 || //常に更新設定
1785 (MES[ch_no[com_mode]-1].err_status & ERR_FLOW_CONT) == 0){ //流量エラー無し
1786 if(RX_buf[com_mode][8] == 0x2c){ // 0〜2はFWDのデータ
1787 ofs = RX_buf[com_mode][7] - '0';
1788 if(ofs == 0) {
1789 for(l = 0; l < 300; l++){
1790 fow_wave_data[l] = MES[ch_no[com_mode]-1].fow_data[l];
1791 }
1792 }
1793 }else{ // 10〜12はREVのデータ
1794 ofs = RX_buf[com_mode][8] - '0';
1795 if(ofs == 0) {
1796 for(l = 0; l < 300; l++){
1797 rev_wave_data[l] = MES[ch_no[com_mode]-1].rev_data[l];
1798 }
1799 }
1800 }
1801 }
1802
1803 if(ofs <= 2) {
1804 for (l = 0; l < 100; l++){
1805 if(RX_buf[com_mode][8] == 0x2c){ //FWDデータ
1806// value = (fow_wave_data[(ofs*100)+l] - AD_BASE)/4; //受波波形データ
1807 value = (fow_wave_data[(ofs*100)+l] - AD_BASE)>>4; //受波波形データ(4回分加算してあるので更に4で割って1/16とする)
1808 }else{ //REVデータ
1809// value = (rev_wave_data[(ofs*100)+l] - AD_BASE)/4; //受波波形データ
1810 value = (rev_wave_data[(ofs*100)+l] - AD_BASE)>>4; //受波波形データ(4回分加算してあるので更に4で割って1/16とする)
1811 }
1812 read_change(com_mode,value,0,1);
1813 }
1814 }else{
1815 for (l = 0; l < 100; l++){
1816 value = 0; //受波波形データ
1817 read_change(com_mode,value,0,1);
1818 }
1819 }
1820#endif //MESWAVEXP
1821
1822#endif
1823
1824}

1826/* メーカー設定読出し(SFC9000対応)(R5) */
1827void command_R5 (short com_mode){
1828
1829 short l;
1830 long value;
1831 unsigned short *pt;
1832 short sn_version;
1833 short sn_ver_cal;
1834 char add[20] = {0};
1835
1836 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].wave_vth; //エンプティセンサ判定閾値
1837 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1838
1839 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].correlate_level; //演算異常判定閾値
1840 read_change(com_mode,value,1,2);
1841
1842 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].correlate_time; //演算異常判定回数
1843 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1844
1845 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].balance_level; //波形アンバランス閾値
1846 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1847
1848 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].saturation_level; //AGC不能判定閾値
1849 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1850
1851 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].attenuate_level; //波形減衰判定閾値
1852 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1853
1854 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].gain_step; //ゲインステップ幅
1855 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1856
1857 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].sound_vel_sel; //音速固定or測定
1858 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1859
1860 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].sound_vel_fix; //音速設定
1861 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1862
1863 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].sound_vel_filter; //音速フィルタ時定数
1864 read_change(com_mode,value,1,2);
1865
1866 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].viscos_auto; //動粘度固定or測定
1867 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1868
1869 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].drive_pls; //打込みパルス
1870 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1871
1872// value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].atn_gain; //アッテネータゲイン値
1873 value = 0;
1874 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1875
1876 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].fifo_ch_init; //FIFO CH 初期値
1877 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1878
1879 value = SVD[0].cunet_delay; //CUnet 再送信待機時間 ※全CH共通
1880 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1881
1882 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].search_sw; //相関値サーチ無効or有効
1883 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1884
1885 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].damp_mode; //気泡対策モード
1886 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1887
1888 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].corr_up.DWORD; //相関値幅上限値
1889 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1890
1891 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].corr_low.DWORD; //相関値幅下限値
1892 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1893
1894 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].inc; //異常ホールド時間
1895 read_change(com_mode,value,2,2);
1896
1897 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].hldt; //レイトリミットホールドクリア
1898 read_change(com_mode,value,2,2);
1899
1900 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].rlt; //レイトリミット
1901 read_change(com_mode,value,2,2);
1902
1903 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].odpd; //レイトリミット1st
1904 read_change(com_mode,value,2,2);
1905
1906 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].rl1tg; //ターゲット1st
1907 read_change(com_mode,value,2,2);
1908
1909 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].rl1av; //アベレージ1st
1910 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1911
1912 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].odpl; //レイトリミット2nd
1913 read_change(com_mode,value,2,2);
1914
1915 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].rl2tg; //ターゲット2nd
1916 read_change(com_mode,value,2,2);
1917
1918 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].rl2av; //アベレージ2nd
1919 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1920
1921 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].rl2d; //ダンピング倍率
1922 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1923
1924 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].rl2hc; //ホールドクリア
1925 read_change(com_mode,value,1,2);
1926
1927 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].dump_var; //可変ダンピング
1928 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1929
1930 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].dump_mul; //可変ダンピング倍率
1931 read_change(com_mode,value,2,2);
1932
1933 pt = &SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].c_serial[0]; //シリアルナンバー
1934 for (l = 0; l < 8; l++){
1935 sn_version = *pt;
1936 sn_ver_cal = sn_version / 0x0100;
1937 if ( (sn_ver_cal >= 0x30 && sn_ver_cal <= 0x39) || (sn_ver_cal >= 0x41 && sn_ver_cal <= 0x5A) ){ //0-9orA-Z
1938 add[2*l] = sn_ver_cal;
1939 }
1940 sn_ver_cal = sn_version % 0x0100;
1941 if ( (sn_ver_cal >= 0x30 && sn_ver_cal <= 0x39) || (sn_ver_cal >= 0x41 && sn_ver_cal <= 0x5A) ){ //0-9orA-Z
1942 add[2*l + 1] = sn_ver_cal;
1943 }
1944 pt++;
1945 }
1946 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],add,sizeof(add)); //最後尾に読込値追加
1947
1948}

1950/* デバッグモード設定読出し(SFC9000対応)(R6) */
1951void command_R6 (short com_mode){
1952
1953 short value;
1954
1955 value = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].test_enable; //流量出力テストON/OFF
1956 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1957
1958 value = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].test_flow; //流量出力テスト値
1959 read_change(com_mode,value,2,2);
1960
1961 value = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].test_err_enable; //エラーテストON/OFF
1962 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
1963
1964 value = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].test_err_code; //強制エラー種別
1965 read_change(com_mode,value,0,0);
1966}

1968/*******************************************
1969 * Function : command_R7
1970 * Summary : 差分相関測定データ読み出し
1971 * Argument :
1972 * Return :
1973 * Caution : None
1974 * Note : ゼロクロス測定データ読み出しはR3
1975 * *****************************************/
1976void command_R7 (short com_mode){
1977
1978 short l;
1979 long value;
1980 long long diff;
1981 unsigned short err_st;
1982 unsigned long long addit;
1983
1984 if(RX_buf[com_mode][7] != '0'){ //測定時データ
1985
1986 //波形表示(全波形or正常波形)選択
1987 if(RX_buf[com_mode][9] == '0'){MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].wave_monitor_mode = 0;}
1988 else{MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].wave_monitor_mode = 1;}
1989
1990 //返信列作成
1991 TX_buf[com_mode][9] = RX_buf[com_mode][7];
1992 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
1993
1994 //1. 流量[mL/min]
1995 value = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].ml_min_now;
1996 read_change(com_mode,value,2,2);
1997
1998 //2. 流速[m/s]
1999 value = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].flow_vel_c / 100;
2000 read_change(com_mode,value,3,2);
2001
2002 //3. 音速[m/s]
2003 value = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].sound_vel_f;
2004 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
2005
2006 //4. 積算値[mL/min]
2007 addit = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].addit_buff.DWORD / 10000;
2008 read_change(com_mode,addit,3,2);
2009
2010 //5. 受波波形最大値
2011 value = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].rev_max_data;
2012 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
2013
2014 //6.
2015 value = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].rev_min_data;
2016 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
2017
2018 //7. 伝搬時間差[ps]
2019 diff = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].delta_ts_zero * 32;
2020 if (diff > 99999999) {diff = 99999999;}
2021 else if (diff < -99999999) {diff = -99999999;}
2022 read_change(com_mode,diff,0,2);
2023
2024 //8. 相関値幅
2025 value = (MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].correlate * 1000);
2026 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
2027
2028 //9. ゼロ点オフセット
2029 value = (SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_offset - 4000) * 32;
2030 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
2031
2032 //10. status
2033 err_st = MAIN[ch_no[com_mode] -1].err_condition;
2034 read_change0X_status(com_mode,err_st);
2035 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
2036
2037 //11. FIFO受波波形検出位置
2038 if((SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].fix_data & 0x08) != 0){ //固定値設定
2039 if(SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].fix_fifo_no_read == 0){
2040 value = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_fifo_no_read;
2041 }else{
2042 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].fix_fifo_no_read;
2043 }
2044 }else{
2045 value = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].fifo_no_read;
2046 }
2047 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
2048
2049 //12. Gain 1st stage
2050 value = get_attenuator_gain(ch_no[com_mode]-1);
2051 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
2052
2053 //13. Gain 2nd stage
2054 if((SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].fix_data & 0x02) != 0){ //固定値設定
2055 if(SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].fix_amp_gain_rev == 0){
2056 value = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_amp_gain_rev;
2057 }else{
2058 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].fix_amp_gain_rev;
2059 }
2060 }else{
2061 value = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].amp_gain_for;
2062 }
2063 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
2064
2065 //14. FIFO CH
2066 if((SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].fix_data & 0x04) != 0){ //固定値設定
2067 if(SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].fix_fifo_ch_read == 0){
2068 value = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_fifo_ch_read;
2069 }else{
2070 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].fix_fifo_ch_read;
2071 }
2072 }else{
2073 value = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].fifo_ch_read;
2074 }
2075 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
2076
2077 //15. 受波の差(P1-P2)
2078 if(MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].max_point_sub_f >= LIM_OVERFLOW) { value = (LIM_OVERFLOW - 1); }
2079 else if(MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].max_point_sub_f <= -LIM_OVERFLOW) { value = -(LIM_OVERFLOW - 1); }
2080 else { value = MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].max_point_sub_f; }
2081 read_change(com_mode, 0, 0, ADD_NO_CMM);
2082
2083 //16-55. 差分相関値
2084 if(MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].wave_monitor_mode == 0 || //常に更新設定
2085 (MES[ch_no[com_mode]-1].err_status & ERR_FLOW_CONT) == 0){ //流量エラー無し
2086
2087 if((MES[ch_no[com_mode]-1].err_status & ERR_JUDGE_EMPTY) != 0){ //Empty Sensor時 波形データ0
2088 for (l = 0; l < 40; l++){
2089 sum_abs_data[l] = 0; //波形データ0
2090 }
2091 }else{
2092 for (l = 0; l < 40; l++){
2093 sum_abs_data[l] = SAVE[ch_no[com_mode] -1].sum_abs_com[l]; //16-55. 差分相関値
2094 }
2095 }
2096 }
2097
2098 for (l = 0; l < 40; l++){
2099 value = sum_abs_data[l]; //差分相関値
2100 read_change(com_mode,value,0,1);
2101 }
2102 }else{ //ゼロ調整時データ
2103 //波形表示(全波形or正常波形)選択
2104 if(RX_buf[com_mode][9] == '0'){MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].wave_monitor_mode = 0;}
2105 else{MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].wave_monitor_mode = 1;}
2106
2107 //返信列作成
2108 TX_buf[com_mode][9] = RX_buf[com_mode][7];
2109 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
2110
2111 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_flow_qat.DWORD; //流量[mL/min]
2112 read_change(com_mode,value,2,2);
2113
2114 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_flow_vel.DWORD / 100; //流速[m/s]
2115 read_change(com_mode,value,3,2);
2116
2117 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_sound_spd; //音速[m/s]
2118 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
2119
2120 addit = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_addit.DWORD / 10000; //積算値[mL/min]
2121 read_change(com_mode,addit,3,2);
2122
2123 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_wave_max; //受波波形最大値
2124 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
2125
2126 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_wave_min; //受波波形最小値
2127 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
2128
2129 diff = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_delta_ts.DWORD * 32; //伝搬時間差[ps]
2130 if (diff > 99999999) {diff = 99999999;}
2131 else if (diff < -99999999) {diff = -99999999;}
2132 read_change(com_mode,diff,0,2);
2133
2134 value = (SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_correlate * 1000); //相関値幅
2135 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
2136
2137 value = (SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_zero_offset - 4000) * 32; //ゼロ点オフセット
2138 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
2139
2140 err_st = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_condition; //status
2141 read_change0X_status(com_mode,err_st);
2142 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma));
2143
2144 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_fifo_pos; //FIFO受波波形検出位置
2145 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
2146
2147// value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_gain_for; //Gain 1st stage
2148 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_gain_1st; //Gain 1st stage
2149 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
2150
2151// value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_gain_rev; //Gain 2nd stage
2152 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_gain_2nd; //Gain 2nd stage
2153 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
2154
2155 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_fifo_ch; //FIFO CH
2156 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
2157
2158 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_p1p2; //受波の差(P1-P2)
2159 read_change(com_mode,value,0,0);
2160
2161 if((SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_condition & CON_EMPTY) != 0){ //Empty Sensor時 波形データ0
2162 for (l = 0; l < 40; l++){
2163 value = 0; //差分相関値;
2164 read_change(com_mode,value,0,1);
2165 }
2166 }else{
2167 for (l = 0; l < 40; l++){
2168 // value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].zero_sum_abs[l]; //差分相関値;
2169 value = 0;
2170 read_change(com_mode,value,0,1);
2171 }
2172 }
2173 }
2174}

2297 else{MES[pch].wave_monitor_mode = 1;}

2300 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],comma,sizeof(comma)); //最後尾に','追加

2302 }
2303#if 0

2315
2316 if((MES[pch].err_status & ERR_JUDGE_EMPTY) != 0){ //Empty Sensor時 波形データ0
2317 ofs = 3;
2318 }else{
2319 if(RX_buf[com_mode][8] == 0x2c){ // 0〜2はFWDのデータ
2320 ofs = RX_buf[com_mode][7] - '0';
2321 if(ofs == 0) {
2322 for(l = 0; l < 300; l++){
2323 fow_wave_data[l] = MES[pch].fow_data[l];
2324 }
2325 }

2330 rev_wave_data[l] = MES[pch].rev_data[l];
2331 }

2352
2353

2358// value = (fow_wave_data[(ofs*100)+l] - AmpOfs)/4; //受波波形データ

2487
2488 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].drive_freq; //駆動周波数
2489 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
2490
2491 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].start_freq; //サーチ開始周波数
2492 read_change(com_mode,value,0,2);
2493
2494 value = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].stop_freq; //サーチ停止周波数
2495 read_change(com_mode,value,0,0);
2496}

2498/* センサシリアルナンバー読出し(SFC014E互換)(Rn) */
2499 void command_Rn (short com_mode){
2500
2501 short l;
2502 unsigned short *pt;
2503 short sn_version;
2504 short sn_ver_cal;
2505 char add[20] = {0};
2506
2507 pt = &SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].s_serial[0]; //センサシリアルナンバー
2508 for (l = 0; l < 8; l++){
2509 sn_version = *pt;
2510 sn_ver_cal = sn_version / 0x0100;
2511 if ( (sn_ver_cal >= 0x30 && sn_ver_cal <= 0x39) || (sn_ver_cal >= 0x41 && sn_ver_cal <= 0x5A) ){ //0-9orA-Z
2512 add[2*l] = sn_ver_cal;
2513 }
2514 sn_ver_cal = sn_version % 0x0100;
2515 if ( (sn_ver_cal >= 0x30 && sn_ver_cal <= 0x39) || (sn_ver_cal >= 0x41 && sn_ver_cal <= 0x5A) ){ //0-9orA-Z
2516 add[2*l + 1] = sn_ver_cal;
2517 }
2518 pt++;
2519 }
2520 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],add,sizeof(add)); //最後尾に読込値追加
2521}

2577/* ステータス読込（16進4文字）*/
2578void read_change0X_status(short com_mode,unsigned short log_st){
2579
2580 unsigned short log_st_cal;
2581 char add[20] = {0};
2582
2583 log_st_cal = log_st / 0x1000;
2584
2585 if (log_st_cal <=9) add[0] = log_st_cal + 0x30; // 0x30:ASCII→16進数字変換0-9
2586 else /*A-F*/ add[0] = log_st_cal + 0x37; // 0x37:ASCII→16進数字変換A-F
2587
2588 log_st_cal = (log_st % 0x1000) / 0x100;
2589 if (log_st_cal <=9) add[1] = log_st_cal + 0x30;
2590 else /*A-F*/ add[1] = log_st_cal + 0x37;
2591
2592 log_st_cal = (log_st % 0x100) / 0x10;
2593 if (log_st_cal <=9) add[2] = log_st_cal + 0x30;
2594 else /*A-F*/ add[2] = log_st_cal + 0x37;
2595
2596 log_st_cal = log_st % 0x10;
2597 if (log_st_cal <=9) add[3] = log_st_cal + 0x30;
2598 else /*A-F*/ add[3] = log_st_cal + 0x37;
2599
2600 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],add,sizeof(add)); //最後尾に読込値追加
2601
2602}
2603
2604/* ステータス読込（16進2文字）*/
2605void read_change0X_2digit_status(short com_mode,unsigned short log_st){
2606
2607 unsigned short log_st_cal;
2608 char add[20] = {0};
2609
2610 log_st_cal = log_st / 0x10;
2611 if (log_st_cal <=9) add[0] = log_st_cal + 0x30; // 0x30:ASCII→16進数字変換0-9
2612 else /*A-F*/ add[0] = log_st_cal + 0x37; // 0x37:ASCII→16進数字変換A-F
2613
2614 log_st_cal = log_st % 0x10;
2615 if (log_st_cal <=9) add[1] = log_st_cal + 0x30;
2616 else /*A-F*/ add[1] = log_st_cal + 0x37;
2617
2618 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],add,sizeof(add)); //最後尾に読込値追加
2619
2620}
2621
2622/* バージョン読込 */
2623void read_change0X_version(short com_mode,long version){
2624
2625 short z;
2626 long ver_cal;
2627 short level;
2628 char add[20] = {0};
2629 char ver[20] = {0};
2630 unsigned short pow_1;
2631 unsigned short pow_2;
2632
2633 if (version >= 0x0000 && version <= 0x000F) level = 1;
2634 else if (version >= 0x0010 && version <= 0x00FF) level = 2;
2635 else if (version >= 0x0100 && version <= 0x0FFF) level = 3;
2636 else if (version >= 0x1000 && version <= 0xFFFF) level = 4;
2637 else level = 0;
2638
2639 pow_1 = 0x0010;
2640 pow_2 = 0x0001;
2641
2642 for (z = 0; z < level; z++){
2643 ver_cal = ( version % pow_1) / pow_2;
2644 if (ver_cal >= 0 && ver_cal <=9) add[level - z -1] = ver_cal + 0x30; // 0x30:ASCII→16進数字変換0-9
2645 else /*A-F*/ add[level - z -1] = ver_cal + 0x37; // 0x37:ASCII→16進数字変換A-F
2646 pow_1 *= 0x0010;
2647 pow_2 *= 0x0010;
2648 }
2649
2650 ver[0] = add[0];
2651 for(z = 1; z < level; z++){
2652 ver[2*z -1] = 0x2E; // ="."
2653 ver[2*z] = add[z];
2654 }
2655 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],ver,sizeof(ver)); //最後尾に読込値追加
2656
2657}
2658
2659/* バージョン読込 (RVコマンド)*/
2660void read_change0X_versionRV(short com_mode,long version){
2661
2662 short z;
2663 long ver_cal;
2664 short level;
2665 char add[20] = {0};
2666 char ver[20] = {0};
2667 unsigned short pow_1;
2668 unsigned short pow_2;
2669
2670 level = 4;
2671 pow_1 = 0x0010;
2672 pow_2 = 0x0001;
2673
2674 for (z = 0; z < level; z++){
2675 ver_cal = ( version % pow_1) / pow_2;
2676 if (ver_cal >= 0 && ver_cal <=9) add[level - z -1] = ver_cal + 0x30; // 0x30:ASCII→16進数字変換0-9
2677 else /*A-F*/ add[level - z -1] = ver_cal + 0x37; // 0x37:ASCII→16進数字変換A-F
2678 pow_1 *= 0x0010;
2679 pow_2 *= 0x0010;
2680 }
2681
2682 ver[0] = add[0];
2683 ver[1] = add[1];
2684 ver[2] = 0x2E; // ="."
2685 ver[3] = add[2];
2686 ver[4] = add[3];
2687 strncat(TX_buf[com_mode],ver,sizeof(ver)); //最後尾に読込値追加
2688
2689}

2692/****************************************************
2693 * Function : JdgIdxErr
2694 * Summary : デジタルフィルタ配置インデックスの判定
2695 * Argument : Idx -> インデックス
2696 * Return : JdgFlg -> B_OK : 正常
2697 * B_NG : 異常
2698 * Caution : None
2699 * Notes : 新デジタルフィルタ仕様のため、
2700 * 以前に使用していた6,7,8,9,11,16,17,18,19は削除
2701 ****************************************************/
2702short JdgIdxErr(short Idx)
2703{
2704 short JdgFlg = B_OK;
2705
2706 //0~20以外はNG
2707 if((Idx < 0) || (20 < Idx)){
2708 JdgFlg = B_NG;
2709 }
2710 else{
2711 //指定番号は仕様変更のため削除
2712 switch (Idx)
2713 {
2714 case 6:
2715 case 7:
2716 case 8:
2717 case 9:
2718 case 10:
2719 case 11:
2720 case 16:
2721 case 17:
2722 case 18:
2723 case 19:
2724 JdgFlg = B_NG;
2725 break;
2726
2727 default:
2728 JdgFlg = B_OK;
2729 break;
2730 }
2731 }
2732
2733 return JdgFlg;
2734}
2735
2736/****************************************************
2737 * Function : command_Rc
2738 * Summary : デジタルフィルタ係数読み出し
2739 * Argument : com_mode -> 0 : ホスト
2740 * : 1 : メンテ
2741 * Return : void
2742 * Caution : None
2743 * Notes : フォーマットは以下
2744 * : @Rc00x,ii,FCS
2745 * : x -> チャンネル番号
2746 * : ii -> デジタルフィルタインデックス
2747 ****************************************************/
2748void command_Rc(short com_mode)
2749{
2750 short Idx;
2751 unsigned short Cef;
2752 //valueを取得
2753 value_judge(com_mode,7,0);
2754
2755 Idx = (short)value[com_mode];
2756 if(JdgIdxErr(Idx) == B_NG)
2757 {
2758 end_code[com_mode] = FORMAT_ERROR;
2759 }
2760 else
2761 {
2762 switch (Idx)
2763 {
2764 case 0: Cef = FPGA_FILIN0_0; break; /* デジタルフィルタ係数(入力側0) */
2765 case 1: Cef = FPGA_FILIN0_1; break; /* デジタルフィルタ係数(入力側0) */
2766 case 2: Cef = FPGA_FILIN1_0; break; /* デジタルフィルタ係数(入力側1) */
2767 case 3: Cef = FPGA_FILIN1_1; break; /* デジタルフィルタ係数(入力側1) */
2768 case 4: Cef = FPGA_FILIN2_0; break; /* デジタルフィルタ係数(入力側2) */
2769 case 5: Cef = FPGA_FILIN2_1; break; /* デジタルフィルタ係数(入力側2) */
2770// case 6: Cef = FPGA_FILCOE_A3_0; break;
2771// case 7: Cef = FPGA_FILCOE_A3_1; break;
2772// case 8: Cef = FPGA_FILCOE_A4_0; break;
2773// case 9: Cef = FPGA_FILCOE_A4_1; break;
2774 // case 10: Cef = FPGA_FIL_EN; break; /* デジタルフィルタ有効・無効設定 */
2775// case 11: Cef = FPGA_FILCOE_B0_1; break;
2776 case 12: Cef = FPGA_FILOUT1_0; break; /* デジタルフィルタ係数(出力側1) */
2777 case 13: Cef = FPGA_FILOUT1_1; break; /* デジタルフィルタ係数(出力側1) */
2778 case 14: Cef = FPGA_FILOUT2_0; break; /* デジタルフィルタ係数(出力側2) */
2779 case 15: Cef = FPGA_FILOUT2_1; break; /* デジタルフィルタ係数(出力側2) */
2780// case 16: Cef = FPGA_FILCOE_B3_0; break;
2781// case 17: Cef = FPGA_FILCOE_B3_1; break;
2782 case 20: Cef = FPGA_FIL_EN; break; /* デジタルフィルタ有効・無効設定 */
2783 default:
2784 break;
2785 }
2786 read_change(com_mode, Idx, 0, 2);
2787 read_change(com_mode, Cef, 0, 0);
2788 }
2789
2790}

2974/* 口径書込み(Wg) */ //種別0〜5
2975void command_Wg (short com_mode){
2976
2977 value_judge(com_mode,7,0);
2978 if ( ( value[com_mode] >=0 && value[com_mode] <= 5 ) && size[com_mode] == 1 && digit_check[com_mode] <= 0){
2979 /*口径変更時*/
2980 if (SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].sensor_size != value[com_mode]){
2981 InitFifoCh(ch_no[com_mode] - 1, value[com_mode]); /*FIFO CH初期化*/
2982 err_thlevel_init(ch_no[com_mode] -1, value[com_mode]); /*波形異常判定閾値初期化*/
2983 }
2984 SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].sensor_size = value[com_mode]; /*make_viscos_tbl(ch_no[com_mode] -1);*/
2985 }
2986 else if (size[com_mode] != 1 || digit_check[com_mode] > 0){
2987 end_code[com_mode] = FORMAT_ERROR;
2988 }
2989 else{
2990 end_code[com_mode] = SENSORSIZE_ERROR;
2991 }
2992
2993}
2994
2995/* フルスケール書込み(Wr) */ //1〜20000mL/min
2996void command_Wr (short com_mode){
2997
2998 value_judge(com_mode,7,0);
2999 if ( ( value[com_mode] >= 1 && value[com_mode] <= 20000 ) && ( size[com_mode] >= 1 && size[com_mode] <= 5 ) && digit_check[com_mode] <= 0){
3000 SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].max_flow = value[com_mode];
3001 SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].unit = digit_check[com_mode];
3002 }
3003 else if ( size[com_mode] < 1 || size[com_mode] > 5 || digit_check[com_mode] > 0){
3004 end_code[com_mode] = FORMAT_ERROR;
3005 }
3006 else{
3007 end_code[com_mode] = FULLSCALE_ERROR;
3008 }
3009
3010}
3011
3012/* Ｋファクタ書込み(Wk) */ //0.000〜9.999
3013void command_Wk (short com_mode){
3014
3015 value_judge(com_mode,7,3);
3016 if ( ( value[com_mode] >= 0 && value[com_mode] <= 9999 ) && ( size[com_mode] >= 1 && size[com_mode] <= 5 ) && digit_check[com_mode] <= 3){
3017 SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].k_factor = value[com_mode];
3018 }
3019 else if ( size[com_mode] < 1 || size[com_mode] > 5 || digit_check[com_mode] > 3){
3020 end_code[com_mode] = FORMAT_ERROR;
3021 }
3022 else{
3023 end_code[com_mode] = KFACTOR_ERROR;
3024 }
3025
3026}

3028/* ダンピング書込み(Wd) */ //0.0〜25.0sec
3029void command_Wd (short com_mode){
3030

3146/* ユーザーリニアライズ書込み(Wu) */
3147void command_Wu (short com_mode){
3148
3149 short l;
3150 short check;
3151 short linear_point; // リニアライズ用
3152 long linear_check; // リニアライズ大小判定用
3153 unsigned short *pt; // リニアライズ用ポインタ
3154 unsigned short point = 0;
3155
3156 check = 0;
3157 /* 設定値数判定 */ //設定点数 0-15
3158 value_judge(com_mode,7,0);
3159 if (value[com_mode] >= 0 && value[com_mode] <= 15 && (size[com_mode] == 1 || size[com_mode] == 2) && digit_check[com_mode] <= 0){
3160 //point
3161 point = value[com_mode];
3162 point = point << 8;
3163 point &= 0xFF00;
3164
3165 SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].uslnr_num &= 0x00FF; //いったん上位8ビットを落とす
3166 SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].uslnr_num |= point; //上位8bitに設定
3167
3168 linear_point = value[com_mode];
3169 linear_check = -1; //output1 = 0 許容用
3170 /* 出力・入力設定値 分離 */
3171 /* 出力×15 */
3172 pt = &SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].uslnr_out1.WORD.low;
3173 for (l=1; l<=15; l++){ //for-loop
3174 /* 入力値 */
3175 i_num[com_mode]++; // ','の1つ後ろへ移動
3176 value_judge(com_mode,i_num[com_mode],1);
3177 if (digit_check[com_mode] > 1 || size[com_mode] < 1 || size[com_mode] > 7){
3178 end_code[com_mode] = FORMAT_ERROR; //End Code 14 桁数異常・未入力(フォーマットエラー)
3179 break;
3180 } //範囲外 for-loop 脱出
3181 if (value[com_mode] < 0 || value[com_mode] > 200000){
3182 end_code[com_mode] = USERLINEAR_VALUE_ERROR; //End Code 44 流量設定値 数値範囲外入力
3183 break;
3184 } //範囲外 for-loop 脱出
3185 if (l <= linear_point && value[com_mode] <= linear_check){
3186 end_code[com_mode] = USERLINEAR_ORDER_ERROR; //End Code 45 流量設定値 順番不適合
3187 break;
3188 } //範囲外 for-loop 脱出
3189 linear_check = value[com_mode];
3190 *pt = linear_check % 0x10000;
3191 pt++;
3192 linear_check = value[com_mode];
3193 *pt = linear_check / 0x10000;
3194 linear_check = value[com_mode];
3195 pt++;
3196 check++;
3197 }
3198 /* 入力×15 */
3199 if (check == 15){
3200 linear_check = -1; //input1 = 0 許容用
3201 pt = &SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].uslnr_in1.WORD.low;
3202 for (l=1; l<=15; l++){ //for-loop
3203 /* 入力値 */
3204 i_num[com_mode]++; // ','の1つ後ろへ移動
3205 value_judge(com_mode,i_num[com_mode],1);
3206 if (digit_check[com_mode] > 1 || size[com_mode] < 1 || size[com_mode] > 7){
3207 end_code[com_mode] = FORMAT_ERROR; //End Code 14 桁数異常・未入力(フォーマットエラー)
3208 break;
3209 } //範囲外 for-loop 脱出
3210 if (value[com_mode] < 0 || value[com_mode] > 200000){
3211 end_code[com_mode] = USERLINEAR_VALUE_ERROR; //End Code 44 流量設定値 数値範囲外入力
3212 break;
3213 } //範囲外 for-loop 脱出
3214 if (l <= linear_point && value[com_mode] <= linear_check){
3215 end_code[com_mode] = USERLINEAR_ORDER_ERROR; //End Code 45 流量設定値 順番不適合
3216 break;
3217 } //範囲外 for-loop 脱出
3218 linear_check = value[com_mode];
3219 *pt = linear_check % 0x10000;
3220 pt++;
3221 linear_check = value[com_mode];
3222 *pt = linear_check / 0x10000;
3223 linear_check = value[com_mode];
3224 pt++;
3225 } //End Code 00 正常終了15点以内・0-20000.0・数値入力順正常）
3226 }
3227 }
3228 else if ( size[com_mode] < 1 || size[com_mode] > 2 || digit_check[com_mode] > 0){ end_code[com_mode] = FORMAT_ERROR;}
3229 else{ end_code[com_mode] = USERLINEAR_POINT_ERROR;} //End Code 43 = 設定点数異常
3230}

3232/* ユーザーリニアライズ切替え(WU) */
3233void command_WU (short com_mode){
3234
3235 short l;
3236 long value_linear;
3237 short check;
3238 unsigned short *pt; // リニアライズ用ポインタ
3239 unsigned short point = 0;
3240 unsigned short value_high;
3241 unsigned short value_low;
3242
3243 check = 0;
3244 value_judge(com_mode,7,0);
3245 if ( ( value[com_mode] >= 0 && value[com_mode] <= 1 ) && ( size[com_mode] == 1 ) && digit_check[com_mode] <= 0){
3246 //ON
3247 if(value[com_mode] == 1){
3248 /* 出力×5 空確認*/
3249 pt = &SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].uslnr_out1.WORD.low;
3250 for (l = 0; l < 5; l++){
3251 value_low = *pt;
3252 pt++;
3253 value_high = *pt;
3254 value_linear = value_low + value_high * 0x10000;
3255 pt++;
3256 if(value_linear == 0) check++;
3257 }
3258 /* 入力×5 空確認*/
3259 pt = &SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].uslnr_in1.WORD.low;
3260 for (l = 0; l < 5; l++){
3261 value_low = *pt;
3262 pt++;
3263 value_high = *pt;
3264 value_linear = value_low + value_high * 0x10000;
3265 pt++;
3266 if(value_linear == 0) check++;
3267 }
3268
3269 if(check == 0){
3270 point = 5;
3271 point = point << 8;
3272 point &= 0xFF00;
3273
3274 SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].uslnr_num &= 0x00FF; //いったん上位8ビットを落とす
3275 SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].uslnr_num |= point; //上位8bitに設定
3276 }else{
3277 end_code[com_mode] = USERLINEAR_5POINT_EMPTY;
3278 }
3279 }
3280 //OFF
3281 else{
3282 SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].uslnr_num &= 0x00FF; //いったん上位8ビットを落とす
3283 SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].uslnr_num |= 0; //上位8bitに設定
3284 }
3285 }
3286 else if ( size[com_mode] != 1 || digit_check[com_mode] > 0){
3287 end_code[com_mode] = FORMAT_ERROR;
3288 }
3289 else{
3290 end_code[com_mode] = USERLINEAR_5POINT_ERROR;
3291 }
3292}

3489 ch[0] = 0;

3494 ch_number = ch[0] - 0x30;

3497 if ( (value[com_mode] >= 0 && value[com_mode] <= 4000) && ( size[com_mode] >= 1 && size[com_mode] <= 5 ) && digit_check[com_mode] <= 2){

3502 }
3503 check_1++;
3504 }

3506 check_14++;

3509 /* 受波波形最大値 */

3512 SVD[ch_number -1].zero_wave_max = value[com_mode];
3513 check++;

3516 check_14++;

3533 check++;
3534 }
3535 else if ( size[com_mode] < 1 || size[com_mode] > 9 || digit_check[com_mode] > 0){
3536 check_14++;
3537 }
3538 i_num[com_mode]++;
3539 /* FIFO受波波形検出位置 */
3540 value_judge(com_mode,i_num[com_mode],0);
3541 if ( (value[com_mode] >= 0 && value[com_mode] <= 3800) && ( size[com_mode] >= 1 && size[com_mode] <= 4 ) && digit_check[com_mode] <= 0){
3542 SVD[ch_number -1].zero_fifo_pos = value[com_mode];
3543 check++;
3544 }
3545 else if ( size[com_mode] < 1 || size[com_mode] > 4 || digit_check[com_mode] > 0){
3546 check_14++;
3547 }
3548 i_num[com_mode]++;
3549 /* Gain1 */

3551 if ( (value[com_mode] >= 0 && value[com_mode] <= 255) && ( size[com_mode] >= 1 && size[com_mode] <= 3 ) && digit_check[com_mode] <= 0){
3552 SVD[ch_number -1].zero_gain_1st = value[com_mode];
3553 check++;
3554 }
3555 else if ( size[com_mode] < 1 || size[com_mode] > 3 || digit_check[com_mode] > 0){
3556 check_14++;
3557 }
3558 i_num[com_mode]++;
3559 /* Gain2 */

3561 if ( (value[com_mode] >= 0 && value[com_mode] <= 255) && ( size[com_mode] >= 1 && size[com_mode] <= 3 ) && digit_check[com_mode] <= 0){
3562 SVD[ch_number -1].zero_gain_2nd = value[com_mode];
3563 check++;
3564 }

3566 check_14++;

3572 SVD[ch_number -1].zero_p1p2 = value[com_mode];
3573 check++;
3574 }
3575 else if ( size[com_mode] < 1 || size[com_mode] > 2 || digit_check[com_mode] > 0){
3576 check_14++;
3577 }
3578 i_num[com_mode]++;
3579 }
3580 }
3581 /* 合否判定 */
3582 if (check_14 > 0){
3583 end_code[com_mode] = FORMAT_ERROR; //End Code 14 = フォーマットエラー
3584 }
3585 else if (check_1 != ch_z){
3586 end_code[com_mode] = KVISCOSITY_ERROR; //End Code 41 = エラー（動粘度係数）
3587 }
3588 else if (check != 7 * ch_z){
3589 end_code[com_mode] = ZADJ_WRITE_ERROR; //End Code 54 = エラー（ゼロ調整・設定範囲外）
3590 }

3730 ch_z = ch[0] - 0x30;

3895/* 薬液リニアライズモード書込み(Wy) */ //0〜1
3896 void command_Wy (short com_mode){
3897
3898 value_judge(com_mode,7,0);
3899 if ( ( value[com_mode] >= 0 && value[com_mode] <= 1 ) && ( size[com_mode] == 1 ) && digit_check[com_mode] <= 0){
3900 SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].LL_enable = value[com_mode];
3901
3902 /* 薬液リニアライズモードON = 薬液種別判定 */
3903 if(SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].LL_enable == 1){
3904 LLmode_kind(SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].viscos, ch_no[com_mode] -1);
3905 }
3906 }
3907 else if ( size[com_mode] != 1 || digit_check[com_mode] > 0){
3908 end_code[com_mode] = FORMAT_ERROR;
3909 }
3910 else{
3911 end_code[com_mode] = LLMODE_ERROR;
3912 }
3913
3914 RX_buf[com_mode][9] = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].LL_kind / 10 + 0x30;
3915 RX_buf[com_mode][10] = SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].LL_kind % 10 + 0x30;
3916 RX_buf[com_mode][11] = 0x2C; //","
3917}

3990/* メーカー設定書込み(W1) */
3991 void command_W1 (short com_mode){
3992
3993 short z;
3994 short l;
3995 short h;
3996 short serial_size;
3997 short check;
3998 short check_14;
3999 short serial;
4000 unsigned short *pt;
4001 char ver[MES_CHAR_MAX] = {0}; // バージョン読込用
4002
4003 check = 0;
4004 check_14 = 0;
4005 serial_size = 0;
4006
4007 /* 補正入力値判定 */
4008 i_num[com_mode] = 7;
4009 for(l=0; l<5; l++){
4010 value_judge(com_mode,i_num[com_mode],2);
4011 if ( (value[com_mode] >= -9999 && value[com_mode] <= 9999) && ( size[com_mode] >= 1 && size[com_mode] <= 6 ) && digit_check[com_mode] <= 2){
4012 check++;
4013 }
4014 else if ( size[com_mode] < 1 || size[com_mode] > 6 || digit_check[com_mode] > 2){ check_14++;}
4015 i_num[com_mode]++;
4016 }
4017 if (check == 5){
4018 /* シリアルナンバー */
4019 z = 0;
4020 while (RX_buf[com_mode][i_num[com_mode]] != ','){ //データ区切り位置判定
4021 if(i_num[com_mode] >= (MSG_MAX-1)){ //','が最後まで見つからない場合
4022 check_14++;
4023 break;
4024 }
4025 ver[z] = RX_buf[com_mode][i_num[com_mode]];
4026 serial_size++;
4027 i_num[com_mode]++;
4028 z++;
4029 if(z >= MES_CHAR_MAX){ //配列外書込み防止
4030 break;
4031 }
4032 }
4033 pt = &SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].c_serial[0];
4034 if (serial_size % 2 == 0){ //文字数偶数時
4035 for (z = 0; z < serial_size; z = z+2){
4036 serial = ver[z] * 0x0100 + ver[z+1];
4037 *pt = serial;
4038 pt++;
4039 }
4040 for (z = serial_size; z < 16; z = z+2){ //16字未満時 空白代入
4041 serial = 0x2020;
4042 *pt = serial;
4043 pt++;
4044 }
4045 }
4046 else{ //文字数奇数時
4047 for (z = 0; z < serial_size -1; z = z+2){
4048 serial = ver[z] * 0x0100 + ver[z+1];
4049 *pt = serial;
4050 pt++;
4051 }
4052 serial = ver[z] * 0x0100 + 0x20;
4053 *pt = serial;
4054 pt++;
4055 for (z = serial_size +1; z < 16; z = z+2){ //16字未満時 空白代入
4056 serial = 0x2020;
4057 *pt = serial;
4058 pt++;
4059 }
4060 }
4061
4062 for (h = 0; h < MES_CHAR_MAX; h++){ver[h] = 0;}
4063 }
4064 if (check_14 > 0 || serial_size < 0 || serial_size > 16){
4065 end_code[com_mode] = FORMAT_ERROR; //End Code 14 = フォーマットエラー
4066 }
4067 else if (check != 5){
4068 end_code[com_mode] = MAKERSET_ERROR; //End Code 49 = 範囲外指定・桁数異常
4069 }
4070 }
4071
4072/* デバッグモード設定書込み(W2) */
4073 void command_W2 (short com_mode){
4074
4075 /* 流量出力テスト項目判定 */ //種別0〜1
4076 value_judge(com_mode,7,0);
4077 if (value[com_mode] >= 0 && value[com_mode] <= 1 && size[com_mode] == 1){
4078 MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].test_enable = value[com_mode]; //流量出力テスト
4079 i_num[com_mode]++;
4080 /* 出力テスト値判定 */ //0.00〜300.00%
4081 value_judge(com_mode,i_num[com_mode],2);
4082 if ( ( value[com_mode] >= 0 && value[com_mode] <= 30000 ) && ( size[com_mode] >= 1 && size[com_mode] <= 6 ) && digit_check[com_mode] <= 2){
4083 MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].test_flow = value[com_mode]; //流量出力テスト値
4084 i_num[com_mode]++;
4085 /* 出力ポートテスト値判定 */ //種別0〜1
4086 value_judge(com_mode,i_num[com_mode],0);
4087 if (value[com_mode] >= 0 && value[com_mode] <= 1 && size[com_mode] == 1){
4088 MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].test_port_out = value[com_mode]; //出力ポートテスト
4089 }else if (size[com_mode] != 1){
4090 end_code[com_mode] = FORMAT_ERROR;
4091 }else{
4092 end_code[com_mode] = DEBUGMODE_ERROR;
4093 }
4094 }else if ( size[com_mode] < 1 || size[com_mode] > 6 || digit_check[com_mode] > 2){
4095 end_code[com_mode] = FORMAT_ERROR;
4096 }else{
4097 end_code[com_mode] = DEBUGMODE_ERROR;
4098 }
4099 }else if (size[com_mode] != 1){
4100 end_code[com_mode] = FORMAT_ERROR;
4101 }else{
4102 end_code[com_mode] = DEBUGMODE_ERROR;
4103 }
4104
4105 if(MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].test_enable != 0){
4106 action_status_control(ch_no[com_mode]-1,ACT_STS_TEST);
4107 }else{
4108 action_status_control(ch_no[com_mode]-1,ACT_STS_NORMAL);
4109 }
4110 }

4338 if ( ( value[com_mode] >= 0 && value[com_mode] <= 999 ) && ( size[com_mode] >= 1 && size[com_mode] <= 4 ) && digit_check[com_mode] <= 2){
4339 SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].rl2tg = value[com_mode];
4340 check++;
4341 }
4342 else if ( size[com_mode] < 1 || size[com_mode] > 4 || digit_check[com_mode] > 2){ check_14++;}
4343 i_num[com_mode]++;
4344 /* アベレージ2nd */
4345 value_judge(com_mode,i_num[com_mode],0);
4346 if ( (value[com_mode] >= 0 && value[com_mode] <= 255) && ( size[com_mode] >= 1 && size[com_mode] <= 3 ) && digit_check[com_mode] <= 0){
4347 SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].rl2av = value[com_mode];
4348 check++;
4349 }
4350 else if ( size[com_mode] < 1 || size[com_mode] > 3 || digit_check[com_mode] > 0){ check_14++;}
4351 i_num[com_mode]++;
4352 /* ダンピング倍率 */
4353 value_judge(com_mode,i_num[com_mode],0);
4354 if ( (value[com_mode] >= 0 && value[com_mode] <= 255) && ( size[com_mode] >= 1 && size[com_mode] <= 3 ) && digit_check[com_mode] <= 0){
4355 SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].rl2d = value[com_mode];
4356 check++;
4357 }
4358 else if ( size[com_mode] < 1 || size[com_mode] > 3 || digit_check[com_mode] > 0){ check_14++;}
4359 i_num[com_mode]++;
4360 /* ホールドクリア */
4361 value_judge(com_mode,i_num[com_mode],1);
4362 if ( ( value[com_mode] >= 0 && value[com_mode] <= 99 ) && ( size[com_mode] >= 1 && size[com_mode] <= 3 ) && digit_check[com_mode] <= 1){
4363 SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].rl2hc = value[com_mode];
4364 check++;
4365 }
4366 else if ( size[com_mode] < 1 || size[com_mode] > 3 || digit_check[com_mode] > 1){ check_14++;}
4367 i_num[com_mode]++;
4368 /* 可変ダンピング */
4369 value_judge(com_mode,i_num[com_mode],0);
4370 if ( (value[com_mode] >= 0 && value[com_mode] <= 255) && ( size[com_mode] >= 1 && size[com_mode] <= 3 ) && digit_check[com_mode] <= 0){
4371 SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].dump_var = value[com_mode];
4372 check++;
4373 }
4374 else if ( size[com_mode] < 1 || size[com_mode] > 3 || digit_check[com_mode] > 0){ check_14++;}
4375 i_num[com_mode]++;
4376 /* 可変ダンピング倍率 */
4377 value_judge(com_mode,i_num[com_mode],2);
4378 if ( (value[com_mode] >= 0 && value[com_mode] <= 10000) && ( size[com_mode] >= 1 && size[com_mode] <= 6 ) && digit_check[com_mode] <= 2){
4379 SVD[ch_no[com_mode] -1].dump_mul = value[com_mode];
4380 check++;
4381 }
4382 else if ( size[com_mode] < 1 || size[com_mode] > 6 || digit_check[com_mode] > 2){ check_14++;}
4383 i_num[com_mode]++;
4384
4385 if (check == 32){
4386 /* シリアルナンバー */
4387 z = 0;
4388 while (RX_buf[com_mode][i_num[com_mode]] != ','){ //データ区切り位置判定
4389 if(i_num[com_mode] >= (MSG_MAX-1)){ //','が最後まで見つからない場合
4390 check_14++;
4391 break;
4392 }
4393 ver[z] = RX_buf[com_mode][i_num[com_mode]];
4394 serial_size++;
4395 i_num[com_mode]++;
4396 z++;
4397 if(z >= MES_CHAR_MAX){ //配列外書込み防止
4398 break;
4399 }
4400 }
4401 for(l = 0; l < 6; l++){
4402 pt = &SVD[l].c_serial[0];
4403 if (serial_size % 2 == 0){ //文字数偶数時
4404 for (z = 0; z < serial_size; z = z+2){
4405 serial = ver[z] * 0x0100 + ver[z+1];
4406 *pt = serial;
4407 pt++;
4408 }
4409 for (z = serial_size; z < 16; z = z+2){ //16字未満時 空白代入
4410 serial = 0x2020;
4411 *pt = serial;
4412 pt++;
4413 }
4414 }
4415 else{ //文字数奇数時
4416 for (z = 0; z < serial_size -1; z = z+2){
4417 serial = ver[z] * 0x0100 + ver[z+1];
4418 *pt = serial;
4419 pt++;
4420 }
4421 serial = ver[z] * 0x0100 + 0x20;
4422 *pt = serial;
4423 pt++;
4424 for (z = serial_size +1; z < 16; z = z+2){ //16字未満時 空白代入
4425 serial = 0x2020;
4426 *pt = serial;
4427 pt++;
4428 }
4429 }
4430 }
4431 for (h = 0; h < MES_CHAR_MAX; h++){ver[h] = 0;}
4432 }
4433 if (check_14 > 0 || serial_size < 0 || serial_size > 16){
4434 end_code[com_mode] = FORMAT_ERROR; //End Code 14 = フォーマットエラー
4435 }
4436 else if (check != 32){
4437 end_code[com_mode] = MAKERSET_ERROR; //End Code 49 = 範囲外指定・桁数異常
4438 }
4439}

4441/* デバッグモード設定書込み(SFC9000対応)(W6) */
4442void command_W6 (short com_mode){
4443
4444 /* 流量出力テストON/OFF */ //種別0〜1
4445 value_judge(com_mode,7,0);
4446 if (value[com_mode] >= 0 && value[com_mode] <= 1 && size[com_mode] == 1){
4447 MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].test_enable = value[com_mode];
4448 i_num[com_mode]++;
4449 /* 出力テスト値判定 */ //0.00〜300.00%
4450 value_judge(com_mode,i_num[com_mode],2);
4451 if ( ( value[com_mode] >= 0 && value[com_mode] <= 30000 ) && ( size[com_mode] >= 1 && size[com_mode] <= 6 ) && digit_check[com_mode] <= 2){
4452 MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].test_flow = value[com_mode];// * 100; //流量出力テスト値
4453 i_num[com_mode]++;
4454 /* エラーテストON/OFF */ //種別0〜1
4455 value_judge(com_mode,i_num[com_mode],0);
4456 if (value[com_mode] >= 0 && value[com_mode] <= 1 && size[com_mode] == 1){
4457 MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].test_err_enable = value[com_mode];
4458 i_num[com_mode]++;
4459 /* 強制エラー種別 */
4460 value_judge(com_mode,i_num[com_mode],0);
4461 if( (value[com_mode] >= 0 && value[com_mode] <= 99) && ( size[com_mode] >= 1 && size[com_mode] <= 2 ) ){
4462 MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].test_err_code = value[com_mode];
4463 }else if ( size[com_mode] < 1 || size[com_mode] > 2){
4464 end_code[com_mode] = FORMAT_ERROR;
4465 }else{
4466 end_code[com_mode] = DEBUGMODE_ERROR;
4467 }
4468 }else if (size[com_mode] != 1){
4469 end_code[com_mode] = FORMAT_ERROR;
4470 }else{
4471 end_code[com_mode] = DEBUGMODE_ERROR;
4472 }
4473 }else if ( size[com_mode] < 1 || size[com_mode] > 6 || digit_check[com_mode] > 2){
4474 end_code[com_mode] = FORMAT_ERROR;
4475 }else{
4476 end_code[com_mode] = DEBUGMODE_ERROR;
4477 }
4478 }else if (size[com_mode] != 1){
4479 end_code[com_mode] = FORMAT_ERROR;
4480 }else{
4481 end_code[com_mode] = DEBUGMODE_ERROR;
4482 }
4483
4484 if(MES[ch_no[com_mode] -1].test_enable != 0){
4485 action_status_control(ch_no[com_mode]-1,ACT_STS_TEST);
4486 }else{
4487 action_status_control(ch_no[com_mode]-1,ACT_STS_NORMAL);
4488 }
4489}

4692/* ゼロ調整詳細データ書込み(SFC9000対応)(W7) */

4694
4695 short z;
4696 short l;
4697 short h;

4699 short check_14;

4728 check++;
4729 }
